  <entry>
    <title>树莓派初始化</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/02/15/%E6%A0%91%E8%8E%93%E6%B4%BE%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/02/15/%E6%A0%91%E8%8E%93%E6%B4%BE%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8B%E5%8C%96/</id>
    <published>2021-02-14T16:39:06.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-02-14T19:10:51.501Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="磁盘初始化"><a class="header-anchor" href="#磁盘初始化">¶</a>磁盘初始化</h2><p>windows下下载sandisk官方软件sd card formatter进行格式化。</p><ul><li>如果用来烧录树莓派系统的tf存储卡已经使用过，格式化类型选择overwrite format/格式化。</li><li>如果是一块全新的tf存储卡，格式化类型使用quick format/快速格式化即可。</li><li>快速格式化只会删除磁盘上文件，格式化会完全扫描磁盘并将磁盘重新分道分簇。</li></ul><h2 id="烧录系统"><a class="header-anchor" href="#烧录系统">¶</a>烧录系统</h2><p>对于没有linux经验的用户，建议使用树莓派官方的raspbian/raspberry os系统。其他用户根据自己需求和习惯选择系统即可。</p><p>下载好系统的img镜像文件后，windows环境下使用win32DiskImager进行烧录。</p><h2 id="开机前准备"><a class="header-anchor" href="#开机前准备">¶</a>开机前准备</h2><ul><li><p>烧录后的磁盘根目录新建名为ssh的空文件，开机后sshd服务会自动开启</p></li><li><p><code>如果使用网线连接树莓派则可以略过这一步</code></p><p>烧录后的磁盘根目录新建wpa_supplicant.conf，内容填充如下</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ctrl_interface=DIR=/var/run/wpa_supplicant GROUP=netdev</span><br><span class="line">update_config=1</span><br><span class="line">country=&lt;Insert country code here&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">network={</span><br><span class="line"> ssid="&lt;Name of your WiFi&gt;"</span><br><span class="line"> psk="&lt;Password for your WiFi&gt;"</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><code>&lt;Insert country code here&gt;</code> 是地区代码，换成 <code>CN</code> （CN 指中国大陆）即可。</p><blockquote><p>在 <a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.iso.org/obp/ui/">https://www.iso.org/obp/ui/</a> 这个地址可以查看所有地区代码</p></blockquote><p>一些注意事项： 1. 最好填 2.4G 的 WiFi，网卡兼容性更好</p><h5 id="额外注意事项"><a class="header-anchor" href="#额外注意事项">¶</a>额外注意事项</h5><ol><li>如果 WiFi 不需要密码，则需要配置 <code>key_mgmt=NONE</code>，比如：</li></ol><figure class="highlight text"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">network={</span><br><span class="line">    ssid="testing"</span><br><span class="line">    key_mgmt=NONE</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><ol start="2"><li>有些 WiFi 设置了隐藏，则需要配置 <code>scan_ssid=1</code>，比如：</li></ol><figure class="highlight text"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">network={</span><br><span class="line">    ssid="yourHiddenSSID"</span><br><span class="line">    scan_ssid=1</span><br><span class="line">    psk="Your_wifi_password"</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><ol start="3"><li>树莓派可以同时配置多个 WiFi，只需要配置多个 <code>network</code> 即可，比如：</li></ol><figure class="highlight text"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">network={</span><br><span class="line">    ssid="SchoolNetworkSSID"</span><br><span class="line">    psk="passwordSchool"</span><br><span class="line">    priority=1</span><br><span class="line">    id_str="school"</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">network={</span><br><span class="line">    ssid="HomeNetworkSSID"</span><br><span class="line">    psk="passwordHome"</span><br><span class="line">    priority=2</span><br><span class="line">    id_str="home"</span><br><span class="line">}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><code>id_str</code> 是标识符。<code>priority</code> 是优先级，越大优先级越高。</p></li></ul><h2 id="将存储卡插入树莓派背部卡槽中开机"><a class="header-anchor" href="#将存储卡插入树莓派背部卡槽中开机">¶</a>将存储卡插入树莓派背部卡槽中开机</h2><h2 id="环境部署"><a class="header-anchor" href="#环境部署">¶</a>环境部署</h2><h5 id="默认配置"><a class="header-anchor" href="#默认配置">¶</a>默认配置</h5><p>raspberry os 默认账户为pi，密码为raspberry</p><h5 id="dhcp固定ip"><a class="header-anchor" href="#dhcp固定ip">¶</a>dhcp固定ip</h5><p><code>vim /etc/dhcpcd.conf</code></p><p>文件末尾追加</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">interface eth0</span><br><span class="line"># 有线网卡</span><br><span class="line">static ip_address={{ 固定ip }}/{{ 子网掩码 }}</span><br><span class="line">static routers={{ 本地路由器地址 }}</span><br><span class="line">static domain_name_servers=192.168.123.1 119.29.29.29</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">interface wlan0</span><br><span class="line"># 无线网卡</span><br><span class="line">static ip_address={{ 固定ip }}/{{ 子网掩码 }}</span><br><span class="line">static routers={{ 本地路由器地址 }}</span><br><span class="line">static domain_name_servers={{ 本地路由器地址 }} {{ 根据自己情况选择合适的dns根服务器地址 }}</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><code>sudo reboot</code>重启树莓派生效</p><h5 id="更换apt源"><a class="header-anchor" href="#更换apt源">¶</a>更换apt源</h5><p><code>vim /etc/apt/sources.list</code></p><p>建议中科大apt源，文件中追加</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deb https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic-updates main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic-updates main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic-backports main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic-backports main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic-security main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic-security main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic-proposed main restricted universe multiverse</span><br><span class="line">deb-src https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/ubuntu/ bionic-proposed main restricted universe multiverse</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><h5 id="安装vim"><a class="header-anchor" href="#安装vim">¶</a>安装vim</h5><p><code>sudo apt-get uninstall vim-common</code>先卸载树莓派原生vim</p><p><code>sudo apt-get install vim</code> 再重新安装vim</p><h5 id="安装远程桌面管理（这里仅以xrdp为例，其余还有vnc等）"><a class="header-anchor" href="#安装远程桌面管理（这里仅以xrdp为例，其余还有vnc等）">¶</a>安装远程桌面管理（这里仅以xrdp为例，其余还有vnc等）</h5><p><code>sudo apt-get install xrdp</code> 安装xrdp</p><p>之后可以通过windows自带的远程桌面进行连接</p><p>账户名密码为树莓派账户名密码</p><p>如果以root账户登录，部分功能会隐，固不建议使用root账户远程连接树莓派</p><h5 id="启用root账户"><a class="header-anchor" href="#启用root账户">¶</a>启用root账户</h5><p><code>sudo passwd</code>先为root账户设置密码</p><p>之后可以在树莓派终端中使用su命令进入root账户，也可以使用root和密码直接登录root账户</p><h5 id="（可选-添加ssh-authorized-keys"><a class="header-anchor" href="#（可选-添加ssh-authorized-keys">¶</a>（可选)添加ssh authorized_keys</h5><h5 id="（可选）禁用root账户密码登录"><a class="header-anchor" href="#（可选）禁用root账户密码登录">¶</a>（可选）禁用root账户密码登录</h5><h5 id="可选-调整树莓派默认频率和内核电压"><a class="header-anchor" href="#可选-调整树莓派默认频率和内核电压">¶</a>(可选)调整树莓派默认频率和内核电压</h5><p>树莓派默认频率只有700hz，使用桌面时会有卡顿现象。</p><p>需要拔出存储卡使用读卡器连接至电脑，修改config文件中默认主频保证性能</p><p>如果调高主频，内核电压也需要相应的提高，否则主频太高电压不足将无法工作</p><p>当然提高内核电压相应的散热措施也需要做好</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">default. arm_freq=1000</span><br><span class="line">over_voltage=4</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;磁盘初始化&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;header-anchor&quot; href=&quot;#磁盘初始化&quot;&gt;¶&lt;/a&gt;磁盘初始化&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;windows下下载sandisk官方软件sd card formatter进行格式化。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;如果用来烧录树莓派</summary>
      
    
    
    
